Company Overview of Nantucket Allserve, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Nantucket Allserve, Inc. produces and sells juices and juice cocktails. Its products include squeezed nectars lemonades and teas, and organic juices. The company also operates a juice bar in Nantucket, Massachusetts. Nantucket Allserve sells its products through bagel shops, delis, convenience stores, and grocery stores in the United States. The company was founded in 1989 and is based in Rye Brook, New York. Nantucket Allserve, Inc. operates as a subsidiary of Dr Pepper Snapple Group, Inc.


45 Dunster StreetCambridge, MA 02138United StatesFounded in 1989



